yle=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 24px;\">有些妈妈在选择DHA经常会有疑问，到底是海藻油好还是鱼油好？掌柜给出明确的答案：鱼油DHA要比海藻油DHA要好！在欧美发达国家，市面上最流行的DHA是鱼油DHA，而海藻油的DHA并没有在美国和加拿大市面的药房销售，海藻油DHA甚至不能在加拿大销售。原因只有一个，就是不符合使用的安全标准。而千百年来，作为人类主食的鱼更加安全可靠，大家都知道吃鱼可以补脑，而干净和高纯度的鱼油更是补充孕产期DHA的最佳选择！而海藻油的DHA在欧美绝对不受欢迎，跑回去中国大吹特吹，确实是无良!</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">医学证明EPA的衍生物二十碳烷酸，其免疫调节剂炎症反应调节的作用，对人体是不可或缺的!</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">【购前知悉】</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">1、关于包装：经常购买国外产品的顾客应该都知道，国外产品经常会更换包装。所以请以实际收到的包装为准哦，谢谢您的谅解！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 15pt 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">2、关于产品：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">软糖会黏在一起，是正常的，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">因运输或</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">气候原因</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">都</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">有可能会引起糖粒粘连，轻轻分开即可。请保存于阴凉干燥处，室温存放</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">。另外</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">软糖产品在冬天感觉会硬一点</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14pt;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 15pt 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"http://qxu1606830112.68dsw.com/images/upload/Image/27.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 15pt 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i3/709293375/TB20vKQdFXXXXc3XXXXXXXXXXXX_!!709293375.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; margin: 13.45pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">【</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background-image: initial; backg