'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: ''lucida grande verdana''; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\">为大家推荐一款冬季的美味饮品，<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">雀巢Carnation的这款热巧冲饮，味道香醇浓郁，没有瑞士小姐那么甜腻，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">曾经以为瑞士小姐是最好喝的热巧，喝过这个之后，发现更胜一筹！</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: ''lucida grande verdana''; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: ''lucida grande verdana''; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\">一袋28g，说明上写的加175ml水，我试过冲了满满一马克杯，300ml的水量都有了，<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">味道还是那么醇厚，可以根据个人口味适量调整~</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">独立的包装随身携带超方便，家里、办公室，想喝了冲一杯，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">不止是美味的享受，更能放松心情、提神醒脑~</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">本品是用纯正可可制作，不含反式脂肪酸，安全可靠，欢迎亲们品尝哦~</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">相信你们喝过之后，也会像我一样爱上它的味道O(&cap;_&cap;)O</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: ''lucida grande verdana''; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 63, 4);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>【产品介绍】：雀巢热巧克力粉（袋装）携带方便，冲饮简单，香浓美味，是欧美最畅销的饮料之一。要冲饮时只需开水冲泡并用小勺轻轻搅拌，一杯香浓美味的热巧克力即可享用。在欧美，人们随时随地都会冲饮一杯雀巢热巧克力――或是工作间歇享用一下这独特的香浓美味放松一会儿心情，或是加班加点时用它来提神醒脑，或是读书看报时不经意地品上一口，或是亲朋好友聚会时热腾腾的巧克力衬托出热烈诚挚的气氛。</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Nestle雀巢Carnation即冲速溶热巧克力1400g</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 123, 173);\"><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>冬天冲上一杯热热的香浓的热巧克力</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 123, 173);\"><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>暖暖哒幸福感爆棚~~</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://qxu1606830112.68dsw.com/images/upload/Image/%E7%83%AD%E5%B7%A7%E5%85%8B%E5%8A%9B4.jpg\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(194, 123, 173);\"><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">先给大家推荐几个热巧克力的冲饮方法：</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 123, 173);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1. 就是直接开水冲印，非常美味香浓。</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 123, 173);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">2. 热水冲，即溶的，然后加入一些牛奶，更加香滑。</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 123, 173);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">3. 和咖啡冲在一起，然后加一些糖和奶。</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 123, 173);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">4. 热巧克力还可以和即溶的奶茶一起冲饮。</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 123, 173);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">反正就是百搭，自己随心所欲，带给自己和家人朋友热热的美味~~</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"http://qxu1606830112.68dsw.com/images/upload/Image/%E7%83%AD%E5%B7%A7%E5%85%8B%E5%8A%9B7.jpg\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 123, 173);\"><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">每盒装内含50小包，即冲饮50杯，每包28克。</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 123, 173);\"><span style=\"font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">净含量1400克 （近3斤），</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194